Package: atspR
Title: Automated Time-Series Preprocessing in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Data", "Scientist", email = "ds@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An automated preprocessing pipeline for time-series and tabular data.
    Provides tools for standardising missing indicators, coercing column types,
    filling temporal gaps, imputing missing values (linear interpolation and KNN
    fitted on training data only), leakage-free temporal train/test splitting,
    feature scaling (Min-Max, Z-score, Robust with automatic method selection),
    k-fold cross-validation, and rich visual diagnostics. All pipeline steps are
    designed to prevent data leakage between training and test sets.
